<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="comment-v">comment <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'kɒment/    美 /'kɑːment/  </p>
<p>(remark)</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-vi-vt">1.★ <strong>vi &amp; vt 评论；批评：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They are always <strong>commenting on / upon</strong> what I’m wearing.
他们总是对我的穿着评头论足。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The discovery is hardly commented by the press.
这个发现新闻界几乎未作评论。</p></div></div>